    {
      "chinese": "水雲三星是指虎頭山、鳥嘴山和橫龍山，是瑪督烏瓦爾語的稱呼。虎頭山是當中最高的山，高達1492公尺，山形似臥虎，山勢格外險峻。",
      "ab": "san maha’ Sweiyunsansing ga, Tinul, Camaputing ru Cawasiq. yani ku’ kai’ nku’ Matu’uwal kahabag. Tinul ga yani capaang na ibabawiq nku’ Sweiyunsansing. kii’ humaynas cu’ magalpu cu’ kabhul ru sapat cu’ kabhul kinibabawiq. tiku cinalxan nku’ ragiyax ka hani ga asing ku’ aqli’ ka kiya ’i’ matahunak. magbatunux ru ibabawiq cubalay ku’ luhi nku’ Tinul.",
